cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY. 

The paper proposes a novel agent that learns to drive a vehicle using reinforcement learning and evolutionary strategies. This falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of difference images in the auto-encoder for better representation of the latent space relates to computer vision (cs.CV). The application of the agent to driving a vehicle falls under robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY).
